review_title: Impressed for so little in price!
reviews: So far so good. We do see a pimple coming to a head after applying a patch 2 hours ago. I dont agree with others that they stick perfectly to the skin but stick well enough. Happy with the different size of patches included. They do not cover up well with make up & would look funny going out with one on. I suggest putting them on before bed. So for my review, if you want pimples to come to a head alot faster, avoid picking & avoid scarring - definitely a must buy! They were extremely cheap for 48 patches, seem to be working to bring the pimple to its white head - so would purchase again for such a low price
